# Global Components

## Navbar
- Horizontal nav with logo and links
- Fixed to top

## Button
- Variants: primary, secondary, ghost
- Use accent colors
- Rounded, hover glow

## Card
- Used for projects and team
- Rounded-2xl, shadow-lg
- Optional hover zoom or border highlight

## Modal (Optional)
- Triggered from project/team cards for more info

## Animation
- Prefer Framer Motion
- Use for scroll-in sections and hover effects
